snippet.title: Rise of Incarnates - Zeus Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Rise of Incarnates is officially releasing on Steam on 7/1/2015!

Celebrate with us on our Twitch channel on 7/1 for a livestream with special guests - http://www.twitch.tv/riseofincarnates
